---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main {
				width: calc(100% - 2em);
				max-width: 720px;
				margin: auto;
				padding: 3em 1em;
			}
			.about-intro h2 {
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
				font-style: italic;
				color: var(--accent);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.value-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 2rem;
				margin: 3rem 0;
			}
			.value-item {
				background: var(--accent-bg);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			blockquote {
				font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
				margin: 4rem 0;
				padding: 2rem;
				border-top: 1px solid #eee;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
				color: var(--black);
			}
			.cta-section {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 3rem 0;
			}
			.secondary {
				background-color: transparent !important;
				color: var(--accent) !important;
				border: 1px solid var(--accent);
				margin-left: 1rem;
			}
		/* 버튼을 감싸는 컨테이너 */
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* 기본 버튼 스타일 */
  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* 왼쪽: 짙은 파란색 버튼 (Journal) */
  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #55729e;
    color: white !important;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  /* 오른쪽: 테두리 버튼 (Newsletter) */
  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: white;
    color: #55729e !important;
    border: 2px solid #55729e;
  }

  /* 마우스 올렸을 때 효과 */
  .btn-primary:hover, .btn-secondary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="about-intro">
				<h1>About Me</h1>
				<h2>"I came to Jeju to survive, and I found a way to connect."</h2>
				<p>
					A few years ago, I felt completely isolated—not just from others, but from myself. 
					I moved to Jeju Island seeking a way to heal, and that's where I discovered the power of 
					<strong>objectifying my own mind.</strong>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="core-values">
				<h3>The Pillars of My Journey</h3>
				<div class="value-grid">
					<div class="value-item">
						<h4>Objectivity (Data)</h4>
						<p>By using EEG tools like Muse, I stopped 'feeling' the pain and started 'seeing' it as data. This objectivity was the first step toward freedom.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="value-item">
						<h4>Solitude (Jeju)</h4>
						<p>Jeju's unique environment allowed me to turn my loneliness into a productive solitude, a space where I could finally hear my own voice.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mission">
				<blockquote>
					"I liberate others through my own freedom. Through my writing and voice, I help people discover their own narrative."
				</blockquote>
			</section>

			<section class="cta-section">
				<h3>Join My Journey</h3>
				<p>Let's move from isolation to connection together.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="/blog" class="btn-primary">Read the Lab Journal</a>
<a href="#newsletter" class="btn-secondary">Join Newsletter</a>

<a href="https://newsletter.playideacompany.com" class="btn-secondary">Join Newsletter</a></div>

<section id="newsletter" class="newsletter-card" style="margin-top: 4rem; padding: 3rem 2rem; background-color: #f8fafd; border-radius: 24px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #eef2f7;">
    <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Join the Calm Day Journey</h2>
    <p style="color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        Get insights on data-driven mindfulness and inner peace. 
        Join a community of readers exploring the intersection of logic and soul.
    </p>
    
    <a href="https://newsletter.playideacompany.com" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; background-color: #1a202c; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; transition: transform 0.2s;"
       onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.05)'" 
       onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
       Subscribe on Substack
    </a>
</section>

<script async src="https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js"></script>

			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>